Fix build w/ dietlibc, probably related to implicit glibc include hierarchy:

extras/ata_id/ata_id.o: In function `disk_identify_fixup_uint16':
ata_id.c:(.text+0xd1): undefined reference to `le16toh'

  - Rene Rebe <rene@exactcode.de>

